content: Reached out to friends from Japan. Their insights on market trends are helping shape my recovery strategy. Perspective is everything.
Set up a meeting with a potential investor for my startup idea. They're interested in the AI integration aspect.
Spent the day optimizing my trading bot. It now handles market volatility better. Small wins, big progress.
Had an awkward encounter with a former colleague who didn't recognize me. Guess I've changed more than I thought.
Got a callback for a full-time position at a blockchain firm. They're interested in my quantum computing coursework.
Finalized my startup pitch with my mentor. He's confident it could secure funding. Now, the wait begins.
My trading bot made its first profitable trade. Feels like a birthday present from the universe. This journey is just starting.
